OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774015868
OL,3,CNumber of confirmed cases of
OL,4,Cmeningitis rises to 27 amid outbreak
OL,5,Cin Kent
OL,7,FThe number of confirmed cases of
OL,8,Fmeningitis in Kent has risen to 27,
OL,9,Fthe UK Health Security Agency has
OL,10,Fconfirmed.
OL,12,FAs of 5pm on Wednesday 18 March, 15
OL,13,Flaboratory cases are confirmed and 12
OL,14,Fnotifications remain under
OL,15,Finvestigation.
OL,17,FThe Health Agency said there have been
OL,18,Fno further deaths since the last
OL,19,Fupdate.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
