PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774015868
OL,3,CNumber of confirmed cases of
OL,4,Cmeningitis rises to 27 amid outbreak
OL,5,Cin Kent
OL,7,FCases have been confirmed at two
OL,8,Funiversities - the University of Kent
OL,9,Fand Canterbury Christ Church
OL,10,FUniversity - linked to an outbreak
OL,11,Fthat is thought to have originated at
OL,12,Fa Canterbury nightclub.
OL,14,FTrish Mannes, UKHSA Regional Deputy
OL,15,FDirector for the South East, said:
OL,16,F"Two doses of the MenB vaccine helps
OL,17,Fprotect individuals against
OL,18,Fmeningococcal B disease.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774015868
OL,3,CNumber of confirmed cases of
OL,4,Cmeningitis rises to 27 amid outbreak
OL,5,Cin Kent
OL,7,F"It is important to know that the MenB
OL,8,Fvaccine does not protect against all
OL,9,Fstrains of meningococcal disease, nor
OL,10,Fagainst all infections that can cause
OL,11,Fmeningitis.
OL,13,F"It also does not prevent the bacteria
OL,14,Ffrom being carried and spread in the
OL,15,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774015868
OL,3,CNumber of confirmed cases of
OL,4,Cmeningitis rises to 27 amid outbreak
OL,5,Cin Kent
OL,7,F"It is therefore still hugely
OL,8,Fimportant that people are aware of the
OL,9,Fsigns and symptoms of invasive
OL,10,Fmeningococcal disease, and that they
OL,11,Fseek immediate medical attention if
OL,12,Fthey or anyone they know develops
OL,13,Fthese signs and symptoms.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774015868
OL,3,CNumber of confirmed cases of
OL,4,Cmeningitis rises to 27 amid outbreak
OL,5,Cin Kent
OL,7,F"If you have been offered preventative
OL,8,Fantibiotics, it is strongly
OL,9,Frecommended that you take them
OL,10,Fpromptly. If you are a student at the
OL,11,FUniversity of Kent who is eligible but
OL,12,Fhas since returned home, contact your
OL,13,Flocal GP, who will be able to provide
OL,14,Fadvice and prescribe the appropriate
OL,15,Ftreatment."
OL,17,FTo date, 600 meningitis B vaccines
OL,18,Fhave been administered at the
OL,19,FUniversity of Kent Canterbury campus
OL,20,Fafter hundreds of students joined a
OL,21,Fqueue outside the campus sports centre.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774015868
OL,3,CNumber of confirmed cases of
OL,4,Cmeningitis rises to 27 amid outbreak
OL,5,Cin Kent
OL,7,FThose who have received the jab will
OL,8,Fneed to return for their second dose
OL,9,Fafter a minimum of four weeks, while
OL,10,F6,500 antibiotics have also been given
OL,11,Fout as a precaution, the university
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FIn total, around 5,000 university
OL,15,Fcampus students are eligible for a jab
OL,16,Fand are being urged to come forward
OL,17,Ffor the immediate protection offered
OL,18,Fby antibiotics and longer-term
OL,19,Fprotection from the vaccine.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
